  <bioghist id="aspace_9d1d9b138a3f2722bb368fef00ae8cc7">
    <head>BIOGRAPHICAL NOTE</head>
<p>Dilip Purushottam Chitre was a poet and critic who published in Marathi and English in India's post-independence period, as well as a painter and film-maker.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_32d72ba5303a6152727a64842a0b150f">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Collection consists of literary papers, including typescripts, manuscripts, publications.</p>  </scopecontent>
